{"tid":13623,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[有圖]傳聞日本護士服將用上不透光物料, 網民:降低病患者的生存率","createTime":"2016-11-30T06:45:56.000Z","updateTime":"2016-11-30T08:57:06.000Z","uid":2110,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"83624bc3ff5ac3782181bfd2810a7d86f6e27317","tid":13623,"uid":2110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T06:45:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://qooah.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/JAPAN-NURSE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fqooah.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F11%2FJAPAN-NURSE.jpg&h=fc9093dd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n不知道宅男們對於白色的護士制服有何感想？但原來有網民指日本護士服是有點透光。<br />\n<br />\n為何會知呢？因為日本知名討論區 2ch 有網民表示日本護士服生產商開始生產不透光護士服。但對於這個消息，日本網民的反應出乎意料的大，甚至在 Twitter 上發出多個留言，其中包括 &ldquo;不要剝削大叔們小小期待！&quot;、&quot;會令男性住院者失去希望，不要啊！&quot;。<br />\n<img src=\"http://qooah.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/2016-11-23-20_55_54.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fqooah.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F11%2F2016-11-23-20_55_54.jpg&h=7325d6ae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n而 2ch 的網民反應似乎比較正面，包括 &ldquo;原來護士服是透光的？好想住院啊！&quot;、&quot;改制服會降低病患者的生存率&quot;、&quot;不快點住院便趕不及啊！&quot;。<br />\n<br />\n似乎日本人看得 AV 太多了吧，現實的日本護士服如下圖。。。<br />\n<img src=\"http://qooah.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/Japnurse2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fqooah.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F11%2FJapnurse2.jpg&h=2a26678b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"322ee3f7a30e820f497ad0f01daf1a93733d00b8","tid":13623,"uid":2110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T06:46:18.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://qooah.com/?p=140588\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fqooah.com%2F%3Fp%3D140588&d=%2FPdnyacYoUlJSF57jd07D2N6obqfy%2FNc7jg2IsrTbnE%3D&h=bb0857cf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://qooah.com/?p=140588</a>"},{"pid":"5078d3b4524f5f798e4d0226d3f4d600770b303e","tid":13623,"uid":498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30